'''人民解放游击军'''（{{lang-en|People's Liberation Guerrilla Army}}，缩写为PLGA）是[[印度共产党（毛主义）|印度共产党（毛主义）]]领导的反政府武装。<ref name="centre">{{cite web|url=http://www.hindu.com/2009/06/23/stories/2009062358320100.htm|title=Centre bans CPI (Maoist)|work=The Hindu|date=23 June 2009|accessdate=7 September 2013|archive-date=2013-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016083644/http://www.hindu.com/2009/06/23/stories/2009062358320100.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>致力于通过[[持久人民战争|持久人民战争]]推翻印度政府。<ref name="kishenji">{{cite web|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2010-03-06/india/28147504_1_telugu-deepak-maoists-kishenji|title=Maoists will overthrow govt much before 2050: Kishenji|work=The Times of India|date=6 March 2010|accessdate=1 September 2013|archive-date=2013-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016083356/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2010-03-06/india/28147504_1_telugu-deepak-maoists-kishenji|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==历史==
2000年12月2日，[[印度共产党（马列）人民战争|印度共产党（马列）人民战争]]创建了“人民游击军”（People's Guerrilla Army）。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-12-17/india/35868361_1_mass-contact-programmes-people-s-liberation-guerrilla-army-plga | title=CPI (Maoist) marks PLGA anniversary with mass contact programmes | work=The Times of India | date=17 December 2012 | accessdate=31 August 2013 | archive-date=2013-10-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016084607/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-12-17/india/35868361_1_mass-contact-programmes-people-s-liberation-guerrilla-army-plga | dead-url=no }}</ref>这天是其三位中央委员被杀害的周年忌日。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/formation-of-plga-a-turning-point-in-the-maoist-movement/article931919.ece|title=Formation of PLGA a turning point in the Maoist movement|work=The Hindu|date=5 December 2010|accessdate=1 September 2013|archive-date=2013-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016062532/http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/formation-of-plga-a-turning-point-in-the-maoist-movement/article931919.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2004年，[[印度共产党（马列）人民战争|印度共产党（马列）人民战争]]与[[印度毛主义共产主义中心|印度毛主义共产主义中心]]合并为[[印度共产党（毛主义）|印度共产党（毛主义）]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.in/2004/10/15/stories/2004101502561900.htm|title=PW, MCCI merge to form CPI (Maoist)|work=Business Line|date=15 October 2004|accessdate=1 September 2013}}</ref> 因此，“人民游击军”也与印度毛主义共产主义中心的军事组织“人民解放游击军”合并为新的“人民解放游击军”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.satp.org/satporgtp/countries/india/terroristoutfits/CPI_M.htm|title=Communist Party of India-Maoist (CPI-Maoist)|publisher=satp.org|accessdate=31 August 2013|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126061902/https://www.satp.org/satporgtp/countries/india/terroristoutfits/CPI_M.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==组成==
人民解放游击军由印度共产党（毛主义）中央军事委员会领导。<ref name="guerrilla warfare">{{cite web|url=http://newindianexpress.com/states/kerala/article192205.ece?service=print|title=Dantawade a pointer to Maoist guerrilla warfare|work=The New Indian Express|date=8 April 2010|accessdate=1 September 2013|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115052/http://www.newindianexpress.com/states/kerala/article192205.ece?service=print|dead-url=no}}</ref>

中央技术委员会（Central Technical Committee）负责制造火箭、迫击炮和手榴弹，中央教导组（Central Instruction Team）在全国移动以培训战士使用武器，中央行动组（Central Action Team）直接在该国开展重要行动。<ref name="guerrilla warfare" /> 毛派的武器80％自己制造，其余从印度安全部队抢夺。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-12-21/delhi/35952735_1_maoists-cadres-dandakaranya-bastar|title=‘LTTE training, police ammo strengthened Reds’|publisher=Times of India|date=21 December 2012|accessdate=10 November 2013|archive-date=2013-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110160958/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-12-21/delhi/35952735_1_maoists-cadres-dandakaranya-bastar|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年9月的分析，基于毛派被拦截通讯认为人民解放游击军的武装人员已从10000-12000名<ref name="T-September">{{citation|title=Top Maoist Leader Ganapathi Admits To Leadership Crisis In Party|url=http://www.tehelka.com/top-maoist-leader-ganapathi-admits-to-leadership-crisis-in-party/|author=Ushinor Majumdar|publisher=Tehelka|date=19 September 2013|accessdate=15 October 2013|archive-date=2013-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016003451/http://www.tehelka.com/top-maoist-leader-ganapathi-admits-to-leadership-crisis-in-party/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>下降到8000－9000名。<ref>{{cite news|title=Reds in retreat|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/beyond-business/reds-in-retreat-113092700488_1.html|first1=R.|last1=Krishna Das|first2=Sahil|last2=Makkar|first3=Probal|last3=Basak|first4=Dillip|last4=Satapathy|date=27 September 2013|accessdate=15 October 2013|newspaper=Business Standard|archive-date=2014-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140206203653/http://www.business-standard.com/article/beyond-business/reds-in-retreat-113092700488_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="centre"/><ref name="kishenji"/> 然而，2014年3月，印度著名社会运动家[[盖塔姆·纳拉卡|盖塔姆·纳拉卡]]认为人民解放游击军的实力不但没有下降反而有所上升，他写道，“人民解放游击军从2008年的八个连和十三个排增长到十二个连和超过二十五个排，外加一个供应排。”<ref name="Gautam">{{cite web|title=Ambush amplifies a struggle|url=http://sanhati.com/excerpted/9499/|first=Gautam|last=Navlakha|authorlink=Gautam Navlakha|publisher=Sanhati|date=30 March 2014|accessdate=16 May 2014|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203102324/http://sanhati.com/excerpted/9499/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 人民武装（被称为Jan Militia）约38000人，大多由部族人民组成，以弓箭为武器，据说为人民解放游击军提供后勤支持。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/indepth/features/2013/08/2013812124328669128.html|title=Analysis: India's Maoist challenge|first=Kamal|last=Kumar|publisher=Al Jazeera|date=24 August 2013|accessdate=31 August 2013|archive-date=2014-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116053341/http://www.aljazeera.com/indepth/features/2013/08/2013812124328669128.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 人民解放游击军的成员都是志愿者，没有工资。<ref name="Walking with the Comrades">{{cite web|author-link=Arundhati Roy|url=http://www.outlookindia.com/article.aspx?264738-0|title=Walking with the Comrades|publisher=Outlook|date=29 March 2010|accessdate=15 October 2013|last=Roy|first=Arundhati|quote=It is an entirely voluntary army. Nobody is paid a salary.|archive-date=2013-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015221518/http://www.outlookindia.com/article.aspx?264738-0|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

2010年[[阿兰达蒂·罗伊|阿兰达蒂·罗伊]]访问毛派游击区时注意到，人民解放游击军的45%战士是女性。<ref name="Walking with the Comrades"/> 而2013年9月的一个分析认为，目前该比例已达到60%。<ref name="T-September"/>现在，[[红色走廊|红色走廊]]的27个部门中，有20个部门的领导者是女性。<ref name="Gautam"/>

[[基申吉|基申吉]]是人民解放游击军高层指挥者之一，曾领导了多次袭击。<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Flood|first1=Derek Henry|year=2010|title=Kishenji:A Profile of the Leader of the Indian Maoist Insurgency|journal=Militant Leadership Monitor|publisher=The Jamestown Foundation|volume=1|issue=4|pages=8–11|url=http://www.jamestown.org/uploads/media/Militant_Leadership_Monitor_-_Volume_I__Issue_4.pdf|accessdate=31 August 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110409083455/http://www.jamestown.org/uploads/media/Militant_Leadership_Monitor_-_Volume_I__Issue_4.pdf|archivedate=2011年4月9日}}</ref>

